  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IFeatureModelReader
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FeatureModelReaderIFileWrapper, VelvetFeatureModelReader, XmlFeatureModelReader
    Deprecated. 
    Use IFeatureModelFormat and FileHandler instead.

    @Deprecated
public abstract class AbstractFeatureModelReader
extends java.lang.Object
implements IFeatureModelReader
    Default reader to be extended for each feature model format. If IFile support is needed, the FeatureModelReaderIFileWrapper has to be used.
    Author:
    Thomas Thuem, Marcus Pinnecke (Feature Interface)
